    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Computer storage devices involving no moving parts in which data is stored in non-volatile memory. Information can be written and retrieved to flash drives more quickly than electromechanical hard drives.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
